short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lead Capture is a free tool to extract '@'IGs from a post. Extract and save your leads in txt file

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Free tool to extract the IG who liked a certain Instagram post.

Build your own lead list with Instagram Audiences. Capture the audience that liked the post and save it in a txt file

✦✦✦ You can get customers from Instagram post likes ✦✦✦

▬▬▬▬ How to use the tool? ▬▬▬▬▬
1 - Just add it to your browser and go to the post you want to capture likes. 
2 - Select the post and refresh the screen to see the download button.
3 - You will see one click buttons to get IG list.
4 - It takes a few minutes to complete the extraction and the list will be automatically downloaded to your machine.
